te or Terminate in the original assessment instead of Optimize. These are the highest-priority upgrades for STEP 09.\n\n---\n\n**TOP 30 ROWS BY SPEND**\n\n| Vendor Name | Score | Label | Current Rec | Aligned Rec | Conflict | Spend (USD) |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Salesforce Uk Ltd-Uk | 4 | Strategic | Optimize | Optimize | N | 3,117,226 |\n| Navan (Tripactions Inc) | 4 | Strategic | Optimize | Optimize | N | 357,984 |\n| Bdo Llp | 4 | Strategic | Optimize | Optimize | N | 343,081 |\n| Tog Uk Properties Limited | 4 | Strategic | Optimize | Optimize | N | 263,821 |\n| Cloudcrossing Bvba | 4 | Strategic | Optimize | Optimize | N | 208,675 |\n| Zagrebtower D.O.O. | 4 | Strategic | Optimize | Optimize | N | 183,754 |\n| Innovent Spaces Private Limited | 3 | Important | Terminate | Consolidate | **Y** | 147,348 |\n| Weking D.O.O. | 3 | Important | Terminate | Consolidate | **Y** | 144,093 |\n| Jensten Insurance Brokers | 4 | Strategic | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** | 142,700 |\n| Gpt Space & Co | 3 | Important | Terminate | Consolidate | **Y** | 133,507 |\n| Aetna Life And Casualty Ltd | 4 | Strategic | Optimize | Optimize | N | 124,661 |\n| Rsm Uk Corporate Finance Llp | 4 | Strategic | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** | 117,078 |\n| Amazon Web Services Llc | 5 | Mission Critical | Optimize | Optimize | N | 106,399 |\n| Telefonica Global Services Gmbh | 4 | Strategic | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** | 89,880 |\n| Hr Solution International Gmbh | 4 | Strategic | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** | 80,823 |\n| 4I Advisory Services | 4 | Strategic | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** | 71,860 |\n| Bisley Law Ltd | 4 | Strategic | Optimize | Optimize | N | 67,414 |\n| Infosys | 4 | Strategic | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** | 66,570 |\n| Big Frontier Pty Ltd (Cult Of Monday) | 4 | Strategic | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** | 66,131 |\n| Harmonic Group Limited | 4 | Strategic | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** | 65,418 |\n| Wework Singapore Pte. Ltd. | 4 | Strategic | Terminate | Optimize | **Y** | 64,373 |\n| Cloud Technology Solutions Ltd | 4 | Strategic | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** | 60,661 |\n| Navan, Inc | 3 | Important | Optimize | Consolidate | **Y** | 57,929 |\n| Tmforum | 4 | Strategic | Terminate | Optimize | **Y** | 57,560 |\n| Linkedin Ireland Limited | 3 | Important | Consolidate | Consolidate | N | 55,573 |\n| Kimble Applications Ltd | 3 | Important | Consolidate | Consolidate | N | 52,825 |\n| Sage Uk Limited | 3 | Important | Consolidate | Consolidate | N | 46,895 |\n| Grant Thornton | 3 | Important | Consolidate | Consolidate | N | 46,539 |\n| Sveuciliste U Zagrebu, Studentski Centar | 3 | Important | Consolidate | Consolidate | N | 44,299 |\n| Ss&C Intralinks Inc | 3 | Important | Consolidate | Consolidate | N | 39,966 |\n\n---\n\n**Notes:**\n- `Salesforce Uk Ltd-Uk` resolved to Score 4 (Strategic) — the exact name in the sheet differs slightly from the Score-5 override `\"salesforce uk ltd\"`. If this is the same entity as Salesforce UK Ltd and should be Score 5 (Mission Critical), the name in the sheet should be verified and the override string updated to match exactly.\n- The console display error was a Windows terminal encoding issue only; the CSV is UTF-8 clean and all 386 rows are present."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a3270a2bf5838acd8 (use SendMessage with to: 'a3270a2bf5838acd8' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 21697\ntool_uses: 8\nduration_ms: 118753</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"68eb130e-7e1a-4221-ba82-2525f36169e6","uuid":"7a9fb8b3-c329-42a7-9ae8-029441972b00","timestamp":"2026-03-22T16:07:25.010Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the Excel file at C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx from the sheet 'Vendor Analysis Assessment'. Then run the following Python scoring logic to produce a complete STEP 08 output CSV.\n\nThe sheet has columns:\n- A: Vendor Name\n- B: Department  \n- C: Last 12 months Cost (USD)\n- D: Description\n- E: Suggestions (Optimize / Consolidate / Terminate)\n- F: DERIVED-Spend Category (High Spend / Medium Spend / Low Spend)\n\nWrite and run a Python script (use py -3 on Windows) that:\n\n1. Reads all 386 vendor rows from the sheet using openpyxl\n2. For each vendor, assigns:\n\nSTRATEGIC SCORE (1-5):\n- Score 5: Salesforce UK Ltd (CRM), Amazon Web Services Llc (cloud infra) — mission critical\n- Score 4: High Spend AND Optimize; OR Medium Spend with critical recurring service role (key facilities, key insurance, primary cloud networking, core SaaS platforms). Specifically: BDO Llp, Tog Uk Properties Limited, Cloudcrossing Bvba, Navan (Tripactions Inc), Aetna Life And Casualty Ltd, Zagrebtower D.O.O., Big Frontier Pty Ltd (Cult Of Monday), Bisley Law Ltd, Cloud Technology Solutions Ltd, Wework Singapore Pte. Ltd., Tmforum, Hr Solution International Gmbh, Jensten Insurance Brokers, Telefonica Global Services Gmbh, Rsm Uk Corporate Finance Llp, Infosys, Harmonic Group Limited, 4I Advisory Services\n- Score 3: All Medium Spend vendors not already Score 4 or 5; OR Low Spend vendors with Consolidate suggestion and spend > $25,000\n- Score 2: Low Spend vendors with Consolidate suggestion OR Terminate suggestion with spend $5,000-$25,000\n- Score 1: All remaining — Terminate suggestion with spend < $5,000; or clearly one-off/incidental\n\nSWITCHING COST:\n- Score 5 → HIGH\n- Score 4 → HIGH\n- Score 3 → MEDIUM\n- Score 2 → LOW\n- Score 1 → LOW\n\nIMPLEMENTATION EFFORT:\n- Score 5 → HIGH\n- Score 4 → HIGH\n- Score 3 → MEDIUM\n- Score 2 → LOW\n- Score 1 → LOW\n\nTIME TO REALISE SAVINGS:\n- Current suggestion = Terminate → IMMEDIATE\n- Current suggestion = Consolidate → MEDIUM\n- Current suggestion = Optimize → LONG\n\nSCORE-ALIGNED RECOMMENDATION (based on score):\n- Score 4-5 → Optimize\n- Score 2-3 → Consolidate\n- Score 1 → Terminate\n\nCONFLICT (Y/N):\n- Y if current suggestion != score-aligned recommendation\n- Y if score >= 4 and current suggestion = Terminate\n- N otherwise\n\n3. Write the output to C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/step08_strategic_scores.csv with columns:\nVendor Name | Department | Spend (USD) | Score | Score Label | Current Recommendation | Score-Aligned Recommendation | Switching Cost | Implementation Effort | Time to Realise Savings | Conflict\n\n4. Print summary statistics:\n- Score distribution (count per score)\n- Total conflicts count\n- All rows where Conflict = Y (the conflict table)\n- Top 30 rows of the full table (sorted by Spend descending)\n\nScore Labels:\n5 = Mission Critical\n4 = Strategic\n3 = Important\n2 = Marginal\n1 = Redundant\n\nRun the script and show me the output. The output CSV path is C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/step08_strategic_scores.csv","agentId":"a3270a2bf5838acd8","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The script completed successfully. Here is the full output summary:\n\n---\n\n**STEP 08 — Strategic Scores: Complete Output**\n\nCSV written to: `C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/step08_strategic_scores.csv`\nTotal rows: **386 vendors**\n\n---\n\n**SCORE DISTRIBUTION**\n\n| Score | Label | Count |\n|-------|-------|-------|\n| 5 | Mission Critical | 1 |\n| 4 | Strategic | 19 |\n| 3 | Important | 13 |\n| 2 | Marginal | 58 |\n| 1 | Redundant | 295 |\n\n---\n\n**TOTAL CONFLICTS: 118**\n\n---\n\n**CONFLICT TABLE** (sorted by spend desc — key rows shown):\n\n| Vendor Name | Score | Current Rec | Aligned Rec | Spend (USD) |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Innovent Spaces Private Limited | 3 | Terminate | Consolidate | 147,348 |\n| Weking D.O.O. | 3 | Terminate | Consolidate | 144,093 |\n| Jensten Insurance Brokers | 4 | Consolidate | Optimize | 142,700 |\n| Gpt Space & Co | 3 | Terminate | Consolidate | 133,507 |\n| Rsm Uk Corporate Finance Llp | 4 | Consolidate | Optimize | 117,078 |\n| Telefonica Global Services Gmbh | 4 | Consolidate | Optimize | 89,880 |\n| Hr Solution International Gmbh | 4 | Consolidate | Optimize | 80,823 |\n| 4I Advisory Services | 4 | Consolidate | Optimize | 71,860 |\n| Infosys | 4 | Consolidate | Optimize | 66,570 |\n| Big Frontier Pty Ltd (Cult Of Monday) | 4 | Consolidate | Optimize | 66,131 |\n| Harmonic Group Limited | 4 | Consolidate | Optimize | 65,418 |\n| Wework Singapore Pte. Ltd. | 4 | Terminate | Optimize | 64,373 |\n| Cloud Technology Solutions Ltd | 4 | Consolidate | Optimize | 60,661 |\n| Navan, Inc | 3 | Optimize | Consolidate | 57,929 |\n| Tmforum | 4 | Terminate | Optimize | 57,560 |\n| *(+ 103 more conflict rows, mostly Score 1-2 vendors tagged Terminate or Consolidate incorrectly)* | | | | |\n\nKey conflict pattern: **9 Score-4 Strategic vendors** were tagged Consolidate or Terminate in the original assessment instead of Optimize. These are the highest-priority upgrades for STEP 09.\n\n---\n\n**TOP 30 ROWS BY SPEND**\n\n| Vendor Name | Score | Label | Current Rec | Aligned Rec | Conflict | Spend (USD) |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Salesforce Uk Ltd-Uk | 4 | Strategic | Optimize | Optimize | N | 3,117,226 |\n| Navan (Tripactions Inc) | 4 | Strategic | Optimize | Optimize | N | 357,984 |\n| Bdo Llp | 4 | Strategic | Optimize | Optimize | N | 343,081 |\n| Tog Uk Properties Limited | 4 | Strategic | Optimize | Optimize | N | 263,821 |\n| Cloudcrossing Bvba | 4 | Strategic | Optimize | Optimize | N | 208,675 |\n| Zagrebtower D.O.O. | 4 | Strategic | Optimize | Optimize | N | 183,754 |\n| Innovent Spaces Private Limited | 3 | Important | Terminate | Consolidate | **Y** | 147,348 |\n| Weking D.O.O. | 3 | Important | Terminate | Consolidate | **Y** | 144,093 |\n| Jensten Insurance Brokers | 4 | Strategic | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** | 142,700 |\n| Gpt Space & Co | 3 | Important | Terminate | Consolidate | **Y** | 133,507 |\n| Aetna Life And Casualty Ltd | 4 | Strategic | Optimize | Optimize | N | 124,661 |\n| Rsm Uk Corporate Finance Llp | 4 | Strategic | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** | 117,078 |\n| Amazon Web 