{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01DUZ7RtT6DCYk9S3zUKzTZe","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01W9CUDcx4YMRzo1AXvGZDDH","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\rjega\\.claude\\projects\\C--Users-rjega-vendor-spend-analysis\\memory\\project_step08_strategic_scores.md","content":"---\nname: STEP 08 Strategic Scores\ndescription: Strategic scores (1–5) for all 386 vendors, 118 conflicts flagged; 9 Score-4 vendors need Consolidate→Optimize upgrade; use in STEP 09\ntype: project\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n- **Total vendors scored:** 386\n- **Total conflicts (current rec ≠ score-aligned rec):** 118\n- **Output files:**\n  - CSV: `C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/step08_strategic_scores.csv`\n  - Excel sheet: `STEP08 Strategic Scores` (in main workbook)\n\n## Score Distribution\n\n| Score | Label | Count |\n|-------|-------|-------|\n| 5 | Mission Critical, cannot be replaced | 2 |\n| 4 | Strategic, high switching cost | 18 |\n| 3 | Important but substitutable | 13 |\n| 2 | Marginal value, overlap exists | 58 |\n| 1 | Redundant or low-value | 295 |\n\n## Score 5 — Mission Critical (2 vendors)\n\n| Vendor | Dept | Spend | Current Rec | Conflict |\n|--------|------|-------|-------------|----------|\n| Salesforce Uk Ltd-Uk | Sales | $3,117,226 | Optimize | N ✅ |\n| Amazon Web Services Llc | Engineering | $106,399 | Optimize | N ✅ |\n\n## Score 4 — Strategic (18 vendors, key conflicts)\n\n| Vendor | Spend | Current Rec | Aligned | Conflict |\n|--------|-------|-------------|---------|----------|\n| Navan (Tripactions Inc) | $357,984 | Optimize | Optimize | N |\n| Bdo Llp | $343,081 | Optimize | Optimize | N |\n| Tog Uk Properties Limited | $263,821 | Optimize | Optimize | N |\n| Cloudcrossing Bvba | $208,675 | Optimize | Optimize | N |\n| Zagrebtower D.O.O. | $183,754 | Optimize | Optimize | N |\n| Jensten Insurance Brokers | $142,700 | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** |\n| Aetna Life And Casualty Ltd | $124,661 | Optimize | Optimize | N |\n| Rsm Uk Corporate Finance Llp | $117,078 | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** |\n| Telefonica Global Services Gmbh | $89,880 | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** |\n| Hr Solution International Gmbh | $80,823 | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** |\n| 4I Advisory Services | $71,860 | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** |\n| Bisley Law Ltd | $67,414 | Optimize | Optimize | N |\n| Infosys | $66,570 | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** |\n| Big Frontier Pty Ltd (Cult Of Monday) | $66,131 | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** |\n| Harmonic Group Limited | $65,418 | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** |\n| Wework Singapore Pte. Ltd. | $64,373 | Terminate | Optimize | **Y** |\n| Cloud Technology Solutions Ltd | $60,661 | Consolidate | Optimize | **Y** |\n| Tmforum | $57,560 | Terminate | Optimize | **Y** |\n\n**10 of 18 Score-4 vendors are currently mis-classified (Consolidate or Terminate instead of Optimize)**\n\n## Score 3 — Important but Substitutable (13 vendors, key conflicts)\n\nHigh-value Score-3 conflicts (Terminate → should be Consolidate):\n- Innovent Spaces Private Limited: $147,348 (Terminate → Consolidate)\n- Weking D.O.O.: $144,093 (Terminate → Consolidate)\n- Gpt Space & Co: $133,507 (Terminate → Consolidate)\n- Navan, Inc: $57,929 (Optimize → Consolidate — duplicate AP entity, not strategic in own right)\n\n## Trade-off Parameters Applied\n\n| Score | Switching Cost | Implementation Effort | Time to Realise |\n|-------|---------------|----------------------|-----------------|\n| 5 | HIGH | HIGH | LONG |\n| 4 | HIGH | HIGH | LONG |\n| 3 | MEDIUM | MEDIUM | MEDIUM |\n| 2 | LOW | LOW | IMMEDIATE–MEDIUM |\n| 1 | LOW | LOW | IMMEDIATE |\n\nTime to Realise also driven by recommendation:\n- Terminate → IMMEDIATE (0–3 months)\n- Consolidate → MEDIUM (3–6 months)\n- Optimize → LONG (6–12 months)\n\n## Key Conflict Tiers for Step 09\n\n### Tier A — Score 4 mis-classified as Consolidate/Terminate (10 vendors): HIGH PRIORITY\nUpgrade to Optimize: Jensten, RSM UK, Telefonica, HR Solution GmbH, 4I Advisory, Infosys, Big Frontier, Harmonic, WeWork SG, TMForum\n\n### Tier B — Score 3 mis-classified as Terminate (3 vendors): MEDIUM PRIORITY\nUpgrade to Consolidate: Innovent Spaces ($147K), Weking D.O.O. ($144K), GPT Space ($133K) — all are active co-working/facilities vendors\n\n### Tier C — Score 2/1 over-termination (105 vendors): GOVERNANCE FINDING\n118 total conflicts; bulk are low-spend vendors where Terminate is applied without consolidation evaluation. Flag as portfolio governance gap in Step 09.\n\n## Step 09 Use\n\n1. Upgrade 10 Consolidate/Terminate→Optimize vendors (Tier A) in final recommendation\n2. Salesforce + AWS = Score 5 confirmed; anchor Step 09 strategy around protecting these\n3. 118 conflicts = 31% misalignment — cite as portfolio governance issue in strategy memo\n4. Tier B co-working facilities ($424K combined) = consolidation quick win\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1735,"cache_read_input_tokens":31731,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1735,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"68eb130e-7e1a-4221-ba82-2525f36169e6","uuid":"f801d5cd-b951-494e-a846-80e73271dd1b"}
