mmendation:\n- Terminate → IMMEDIATE (0–3 months)\n- Consolidate → MEDIUM (3–6 months)\n- Optimize → LONG (6–12 months)\n\n## Key Conflict Tiers for Step 09\n\n### Tier A — Score 4 mis-classified as Consolidate/Terminate (10 vendors): HIGH PRIORITY\nUpgrade to Optimize: Jensten, RSM UK, Telefonica, HR Solution GmbH, 4I Advisory, Infosys, Big Frontier, Harmonic, WeWork SG, TMForum\n\n### Tier B — Score 3 mis-classified as Terminate (3 vendors): MEDIUM PRIORITY\nUpgrade to Consolidate: Innovent Spaces ($147K), Weking D.O.O. ($144K), GPT Space ($133K) — all are active co-working/facilities vendors\n\n### Tier C — Score 2/1 over-termination (105 vendors): GOVERNANCE FINDING\n118 total conflicts; bulk are low-spend vendors where Terminate is applied without consolidation evaluation. Flag as portfolio governance gap in Step 09.\n\n## Step 09 Use\n\n1. Upgrade 10 Consolidate/Terminate→Optimize vendors (Tier A) in final recommendation\n2. Salesforce + AWS = Score 5 confirmed; anchor Step 09 strategy around protecting these\n3. 118 conflicts = 31% misalignment — cite as portfolio governance issue in strategy memo\n4. Tier B co-working facilities ($424K combined) = consolidation quick win\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":1,"oldLines":70,"newStart":1,"newLines":96,"lines":[" ---"," name: STEP 08 Strategic Scores","-description: Strategic scores (1–5) for all 386 vendors, 187 conflicts flagged; 9 Score-4 vendors need Consolidate→Optimize upgrade; use in STEP 09","+description: Strategic scores (1–5) for all 386 vendors, 118 conflicts flagged; 9 Score-4 vendors need Consolidate→Optimize upgrade; use in STEP 09"," type: project"," ---"," "," ## Summary"," "," - **Total vendors scored:** 386","-- **Total conflicts (current rec ≠ score-aligned rec):** 187","-- **Output file:** `C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/step08_strategic_scores.csv`","+- **Total conflicts (current rec ≠ score-aligned rec):** 118","+- **Output files:**","+  - CSV: `C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-anal